item.title: How to change Damage
item.dc:creator: @1pure1337 1pure1337
item.description:
@1pure1337 wrote:

go into the “config” folder in your source, and click ‘item’. then hit Ctrl F and type in the name of the item (when you use spaces use _'s) then go to the right of the item, the second or third last one is usually the strength bonus, so replace the number there with whatever bonus you want it to give, save, compile and it should work. any other questions pm me or add my msn in my signature.
